{"tid":2518154,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"據報騰訊與美國監管機構磋商  以保留對Riot Games及Epic Games的持股。","createTime":"2021-05-05T23:20:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T23:44:59.000Z","uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f8c8875c7187def7b175ec8ac5a148e57ac49568","tid":2518154,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T23:20:13.000Z","msg":"外電引述消息人士指，騰訊正與美國外資審議委員會(CFIUS)協商降低風險的措施，以保留集團對美國遊戲開發商Riot Games及Epic Games的持股。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士指，<strong><span class=\"red\">騰訊自去年下半年起持續與CFIUS磋商，CFIUS一直研究兩家遊戲開發商，處理用戶個人數據時，是否因為騰訊的中資背景，而構成國家安全風險。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n消息人士說，Epic Games並未與騰訊共享任何用戶數據。Riot Games指，公司運作獨立於騰訊，並已實施行業領先做法，以保護玩家數據。<br />\n<br />\n騰訊持有Epic Games的40%股份，並於2011年買入Riot Games多數股份，2015年取得公司其餘股份。"},{"pid":"8486db77d1d2f1f558e735bd975ddd37e602cb9e","tid":2518154,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T23:21:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1589450-20210506.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1589450-20210506.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=lnSleIYCVJUMUgC9CFuHQvzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=f64b4fe6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1589450-20210506.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ddf2bf20\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1589450-20210506.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"3160d6de8770cfa7b7cd9fd0873e08b9aacd5514","tid":2518154,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T23:25:11.000Z","msg":"Epic Games經常送GAME<br />\n其實係賄選買票的玩意, 吸引各國後生投票比親共政客"},{"pid":"7c630c6344c960e8a7a0f6e9d32b98a75f370ff7","tid":2518154,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T23:27:06.000Z","msg":"邊使呀，支國人唔係最識得騎劫間公司嘅咩"},{"pid":"a311d363df6625ba6d563e0d65f00a9d8f8efd07","tid":2518154,"uid":374725,"like":1,"disli